BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:[Ocoee Open Gym Volleyball] Open Gym Volleyball
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260721T201500
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260721T223000
UID:Ocoee_Open_Gym_Volleyball-Open_Gym_Volleyball-2026-07-21T20:15:00
DESCRIPTION:Join us every Tuesday night from 8:15 pm to 10:30 pm for open 
 gym volleyball. Our open gym format allows players of all skill levels to 
 enjoy open court time - no teams\, no rosters\, no pressure . Whether you
 ’re new to the sport\, working on technique\, or looking for regular vol
 leyball fun with others\, our gym is ready for you. All participants must 
 have an active daily or annual membership. Register for open gym volleybal
 l .\n\nAnnual court pass available for $35.\n\nRegister: https://secure.re
 c1.com/FL/ocoee-parks-recreation-fl/catalog/index/0679b20b7684e99b55b7c87a
 01b6acfc?filter=c2VhcmNoPSZjYXRlZ29yeSU1QjMyNDg3JTVEPTE=\n\nMore info: htt
 ps://www.ocoee.org/171/Adult-Programs
LOCATION:Jim Beech Recreation Center
URL:https://www.ocoee.org/171/Adult-Programs
END:VEVENT
